frames.caption: A sleek, modern train glides through a snow-covered forest, its warm interior lights contrasting with the cold, snowy landscape. Tall, snow-laden pine trees surround the train, creating a serene winter scene. The train's futuristic design and the glowing tracks add a touch of elegance to the tranquil setting.
